data.key: Any customer with an active HABIBMETRO account can register for this service.

sections.title: Why use the HABIBMETRO Mobile Banking App?

data.key: HABIBMETRO Mobile Banking app gives you 24/7 access to your bank accounts via your smartphones. Now customers can manage their accounts, pay their bills, and transfer funds anytime anywhere while on the go.

sections.title: What is the installment procedure?

data.key: Please access Google Play or App Store or Huawei AppGallery and search for the HABIBMETRO Mobile Banking app through your Android or iOS or Huawei smartphones and click on the 'Install Application' button. once installed, proceed to Sign In.
